dmca.title: DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google: Android Market

works.description:
The work is the Academical English <->
Russian dictionary based on the content of our partner АСТ Пресс-Книга -
one of the biggest publishing houses in Russia. The partner licensed us the
content of the dictionary with the licensing agreement which we will
provide on your request. As usual we are ready with the screen-shots which
we will send to Google Team by e-mail once the complaint is confirmed.
